===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Norman (Masters)}}
Norman forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Norman|Slaking}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Norman became a playable sync pair since the game's release, with him joining the {{player}} after completing the seventh chapter of the [[PML arc]].

In this game, Norman is {{mas|Brendan}}'s father and one of the PML Leaders of the [[Pokémon Masters League]], handing out the {{badge|Patience}} to those who defeat him. He has also made notable appearances in the game's main stories: the PML arc, [[Legendary Adventures]], and the [[villain arc]]. 

